main event: A UFO was sighted over the campus of the University of Southern Alabama in Mobile, Alabama on October 13, 1966.
interesting points: The UFO was circular in shape, about 25-30 feet in diameter and 1/2 feet thick, with a 5-foot probe or antenna on top.
The UFO made straight line maneuvers and turns for about 5 minutes before departing to the north.
The UFO was observed visually without any optical aids and was estimated to be at an angle of elevation of 72 degrees.
The witness, an 18-year-old female freshman student, reported a slight hovering sound that called her attention to the object.
The weather conditions were clear and cloudless with a temperature of 68Â°F.
